'From Squeak4.2 of 4 February 2011 [latest update: #10966] on 3 October 2011 at 1:08:10 pm'!"Change Set:		StrikeFontSet-copy-muDate:			3 October 2011Author:			Masashi UmezawaSalvaged original copy implemention"!!StrikeFontSet methodsFor: 'copying' stamp: 'yo 9/17/2002 17:15'!copy	| s a |	s := self class new.	s name: self name.	s emphasis: self emphasis.	s reset.	a := Array new: fontArray size.	1 to: a size do: [:i |		a at: i put: (fontArray at: i) copy.	].	s fontArray: a.	^ s.! !